name: Comanche's Lovely Eyes
description:
Collection: Oh, Those Eyes!

Comanche's Lovely Eyes is the first in a collection of animal eyes. More will be minted soon. Some of the images will be based upon my original art and some of them will be photographs. This is a photo of my horse's eyes.
I’m @wildozark on Twitter if you’d like to get in touch.

These images will also be available in limited edition real prints. More information about them can be found at wildozark.com/animal-eyes.
